Why did you have to go that far?

29
00:02:34,362 --> 00:02:36,906
I know you made Park Seo-a
spread the video

30
00:02:38,032 --> 00:02:39,659
Ko A-ram backed up to the cloud.

31
00:02:42,328 --> 00:02:43,746
I've been thinking about it,

32
00:02:45,206 --> 00:02:47,125
and it's just too much.

33
00:02:51,880 --> 00:02:54,215
So you weren't just handling
the divorce case.

34
00:02:56,050 --> 00:02:59,512
I wondered how the victims' statements
and the lawsuit

35
00:02:59,596 --> 00:03:01,890
were moving so unusually fast.

36
00:03:01,973 --> 00:03:03,057
It was you.

37
00:03:03,141 --> 00:03:05,810
You won't be able
to escape punishment either,

38
00:03:06,603 --> 00:03:08,438
for instigating those kids.

39
00:03:11,524 --> 00:03:12,692
I don't intend to.

40
00:03:14,527 --> 00:03:16,446
I did something wrong,

41
00:03:16,529 --> 00:03:18,281
so I deserve to be punished.

42
00:03:26,080 --> 00:03:28,583
I don't understand why you're doing this.

43
00:03:29,959 --> 00:03:33,379
Didn't you join Hyun's campaign
because your husband was unfairly blamed

44
00:03:33,463 --> 00:03:35,173
and denied worker's compensation?

45
00:03:36,007 --> 00:03:39,093
Didn't you enter politics
to make things right?

46
00:03:39,177 --> 00:03:41,054
I don't understand how someone like that

47
00:03:41,137 --> 00:03:43,890
could commit a crime
using the president-elect as an excuse.

48
00:03:48,102 --> 00:03:50,188
You know more about me than I thought.

49
00:03:50,271 --> 00:03:53,191
Most lawyers get others
to do the background checks,

50
00:03:53,274 --> 00:03:54,901
but I do it myself.

51
00:03:54,984 --> 00:03:57,445
Just like I did
with Ko A-ram and Park Seo-a.

52
00:03:59,239 --> 00:04:00,949
It wasn't for the president-elect.

53
00:04:01,658 --> 00:04:03,326
It it were,

54
00:04:03,826 --> 00:04:07,747
I wouldn't have pushed
his only daughter that far.

55
00:04:08,665 --> 00:04:10,708
Then who was it for? What was it for?

56
00:04:11,209 --> 00:04:13,628
"Punishment is not what we want."

57
00:04:13,711 --> 00:04:15,296
"We want our family back."

58
00:04:16,756 --> 00:04:19,259
"Revenge is not what I want."

59
00:04:19,842 --> 00:04:22,887
"I want my mom and dad to come back home."

60
00:04:24,180 --> 00:04:27,850
This was your eulogy for your parents
after losing them

61
00:04:27,934 --> 00:04:30,019
to the H Chemical fire in 2012.

62
00:04:38,111 --> 00:04:39,654
You did your research.

63
00:04:41,614 --> 00:04:43,616
Why did you take the divorce case?

64
00:04:44,325 --> 00:04:46,536
Why did you decide
to be on Ms. Cha's side?

65
00:04:49,122 --> 00:04:50,373
What do you want?

66
