00:33:13,866 --> 00:33:16,411
Wrong password.

492
00:33:16,494 --> 00:33:17,537
Please try again.

493
00:33:17,620 --> 00:33:20,707
After three failed attempts,
you cannot re-enter for an hour.

494
00:33:20,790 --> 00:33:24,085
One hour?
It's over if it gets locked for an hour.

495
00:33:39,267 --> 00:33:41,310
Is it six digits, not four?

496
00:33:42,145 --> 00:33:44,397
My electronic door lock is six digits too.

497
00:33:49,610 --> 00:33:51,654
Except for one and nine…

