00:34:47,835 --> 00:34:49,378
Safe unlocked.

513
00:34:49,462 --> 00:34:51,422
The door is opening.

514
00:35:50,982 --> 00:35:53,025
What were you doing in there?

515
00:35:53,109 --> 00:35:54,735
Shush. I…

516
00:35:56,654 --> 00:36:00,616
I took a selfie
to post on my social media.

517
00:36:01,325 --> 00:36:03,536
Don't tell your mom about this.

518
00:36:04,162 --> 00:36:07,498
Right, and I followed your account.
Make sure you follow me back.

519
00:36:11,043 --> 00:36:13,629
Ko A-ram and Park Seo-a
didn't contact you, did they?

520
00:36:17,008 --> 00:36:18,009
No.

521
00:36:18,759 --> 00:36:20,970
They haven't since they were disciplined.

522
00:36:21,971 --> 00:36:25,600
As I said before, if they come
find you or anything, let me know.

523
00:36:25,683 --> 00:36:28,019
I'll deal with them right away, okay?

524
00:36:29,187 --> 00:36:30,271
Lawyer Kang.

